" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Determinant of proximal tubule cell pH",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 436px; height: 229px; background-image: url(data:image/gif;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Effect of lowering the HCO3- concentration and pH in the fluid in the tubular lumen or in the peritubular capillary on the proximal tubular cell pH. Only the change in peritubular capillary pH significantly lowers the cell pH, an effect that appears to be mediated by the Na+:3HCO3- cotransporter.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
